(firstQuint)Study of Sildenafil as a Therapy for Fatigue in Pancreatic Cancer.

 This is a double-blinded, placebo-controlled trial in men and women, 40-75 years old, diagnosed with pancreatic or cholangiocarcinoma cancer.

 Patients will receive placebo or sildenafil daily for 4 weeks during their initial chemotherapy cycle.

